                <br /><br />               
                <p>When you&rsquo;re looking to buy or sell your home, you want to work with an agent who knows more than the neighborhood &ndash; you want someone who knows the area, the market, and how to maximize your benefits on the transaction. As a 20-year resident of Basking Ridge, and a father who&rsquo;s experienced the area&rsquo;s outstanding public schools firsthand, Mark Schottenfeld is the agent to see if you&rsquo;re buying or selling in Somerset County.</p>
                <p>Mark, a Berkshire Hathaway Home Services agent who also covers much of Morris County, has one daughter who recently graduated from Ridge High School, and another entering her junior year. He&rsquo;s seen firsthand the excellence of the local school systems, which is a major draw for families looking to move into the area. With a Master&rsquo;s Degree in Real Estate Finance, he is uniquely positioned to help clients understand and navigate the complex process of buying or selling a home.</p>
